<head>
  <meta name="title" content="Northwest Chimney (the chute above the NW fan apex) (Potter Creek)"/>
  <meta name="description" content="The chimneys existence above the NW apex, the 41 ft climb to an arched cavity, the earth-choked fissure toward the surface and the live pine roots."/>
  <meta name="rights" content="Interpretive: Shaft diameter (unsurveyed), exact profile; a natural conduit, not a human entrance. LAYOUT: global_position/level_order/stream_bbox are interpretive staging for the unified walkable level, not survey"/>
</head>
